## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] MongoDB Seed Script
I will provide a script to populate `customData` for existing campaigns to demonstrate the implementation.

#### [NEW] [seed-custom-fields.js](file:///c:/Users/pratik/MRv5-TSX/MapRecruit.ai-TypeScript-/backend/scripts/seed-custom-fields.js)

The script will:
- Iterate through campaigns for company `6112806bc9147f673d28c6eb`.
- Generate plausible data for each custom field based on its [format](file:///c:/Users/pratik/MRv5-TSX/MapRecruit.ai-TypeScript-/components/ProfileViews.tsx#29-36) (Integer, Float, Text, Date, etc.).
- Update the `customData` field in MongoDB using `updateOne`.

### [Documentation] Implementation Document
This file serves as the core implementation guide for the Campaigns tab custom fields.

