## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] MongoDB Seed Script for Resumes

#### [NEW] [seed-resume-custom-fields.js](file:///c:/Users/pratik/MRv5-TSX/MapRecruit.ai-TypeScript-/backend/scripts/seed-resume-custom-fields.js)

The script:
- Connects to `MRv5.resumesDB`.
- Iterates over resume docs for company `6112806bc9147f673d28c6eb`.
- Builds `customData` with plausible values for all 15 known fields.
- Applies updates with `$set` (non-destructive to existing fields).

