- Query `MRv5.resumesDB` via MCP to confirm `customData` is populated on updated docs.

### Manual
- Open a candidate profile in the app → check **Additional Information** / **TRC Staffing** tabs render the seeded values.

## UI Design Alignment (Existing Design Language)

The Custom Fields page will be realigned with the application's standard design language, focusing on consistency, grounded card layouts, and Emerald-based accents.

### Design Principles
- **Grounding over Glass**: Replace `backdrop-blur` and translucent backgrounds with standard solids (`bg-white` in light mode, `bg-slate-900` in dark mode).
- **Correct Sizing**: Reduce header sizes from `text-4xl/5xl` to `text-2xl` for consistency. Use standard padding (`p-8` for sections).
- **Emerald Accents**: Transition primary buttons and active states to Emerald (`bg-emerald-600`) as seen in Workspace Configurations.
- **Standard Tabs**: Use the application's existing pill-style tab design instead of the custom floating version.
- **Refined Typography**: Use `text-sm font-semibold` for labels and `text-[11px]` for uppercase subheaders.

### Implementation Checklist
- [ ] Remove glassmorphic styles and replace with standard card surfaces.
- [ ] Resize typography (Headers, Labels, Inputs) to match [CampaignSettings](file:///c:/Users/pratik/MRv5-TSX/MapRecruit.ai-TypeScript-/pages/Campaign/Settings/index.tsx#12-645).
- [ ] Implement standard Pill-style Tabs with `bg-slate-100` track.
- [ ] Standardize the Field Editor Drawer with consistent padding and solid backgrounds.
- [ ] Update Badge styles to match the application's existing tag/badge patterns.
